{"tid":2225830,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地仲有啲歌要整.....","createTime":"2020-10-01T15:18:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T15:55:46.000Z","uid":29033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"09414628d31d3b7236f7234d423652203ac874e1","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:18:09.000Z","msg":"加泰人<br />\n日本人<br />\n維吾爾人<br />\n圖博人<br />\n泰國人<br />\n白羅斯人<br />\n美國人<br />\n英國人<br />\n台灣人<br />\n仲有好多好多人有支持香港.......我地唱唔到香港人嘅歌，都要唱其他國家追求民主嘅歌....！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/adria_ballester/status/1311624235853508609?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadria_ballester%2Fstatus%2F1311624235853508609%3Fs%3D21&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=dd1fc1de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fadria_ballester%2Fstatus%2F1311624235853508609%3Fs%3D21&h=1fbcb8eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/adria_ballester/status/1311624235853508609?s=21</a><br />\n加泰人喺中國領事館門口<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1311623880155553792?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1311623880155553792%3Fs%3D21&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=631d4d9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbenedictrogers%2Fstatus%2F1311623880155553792%3Fs%3D21&h=2dfd98fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/benedictrogers/status/1311623880155553792?s=21</a><br />\n英佬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1311642547895246848?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1311642547895246848%3Fs%3D21&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=cae95063\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsolomonyue%2Fstatus%2F1311642547895246848%3Fs%3D21&h=77e391b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/solomonyue/status/1311642547895246848?s=21</a><br />\n美佬佢話葉劉啲奶有問題<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/106682420777263/posts/337648897680613/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F106682420777263%2Fposts%2F337648897680613%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=b17fce96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/106682420777263/posts/337648897680613/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n泰佬<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10156942883281065/?extid=0&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F46251501064%2Fposts%2F10156942883281065%2F%3Fextid%3D0%26d%3Dn&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=f8af33cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/46251501064/posts/10156942883281065/?extid=0&amp;d=n</a><br />\n台佬<br />\n<br />\n不能盡錄......（有閪人會逐條㩒嚟睇哂咩憨鳩）<br />\n<br />\n麻煩第一條加泰一定要睇<br />\n<br />\n小弟不才音樂零蛋，希望香港可以有廣東話版音樂同歌支持返人地，同時提醒自己........<br />\n<br />\n企喺最前線嘅，唔止香港"},{"pid":"d73f2f75faa56fc220fa8f7b8aeef9fc317011f4","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:28:23.000Z","msg":"泰歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://musicofthaifreedom.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmusicofthaifreedom.com%2F&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=0a257222\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://musicofthaifreedom.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n加泰歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elnacional.cat/en/politics/catalan-song-estaca-grand-finale-madrid-march_365209_102.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elnacional.cat%2Fen%2Fpolitics%2Fcatalan-song-estaca-grand-finale-madrid-march_365209_102.html&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=7e09b016\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.elnacional.cat/en/politics/catalan-song-estaca-grand-finale-madrid-march_365209_102.html</a><br />\n<br />\n圖博歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DztgQIJfbtw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDztgQIJfbtw&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=6df8b1b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DztgQIJfbtw</a><br />\n<br />\n泰歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/XKV7Keo68PM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXKV7Keo68PM&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=a0b40497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/XKV7Keo68PM</a><br />\n<br />\n泰文版榮光<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/solidaritywithhk/videos/966850120408495/?vh=e&amp;extid=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsolidaritywithhk%2Fvideos%2F966850120408495%2F%3Fvh%3De%26extid%3D0&d=2MheXYw%2FBwPqfvV%2BE34w1%2BBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=6fa6eb7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/solidaritywithhk/videos/966850120408495/?vh=e&amp;extid=0</a><br />\n<br />\n以上臨時搵，了解唔深入，如果有當地巴絲麻煩真係出聲指條明路行吓<br />\n<br />\n錫晒你哋"},{"pid":"083bdc1c5594f882e66143326cc2b4f16a81a82b","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:28:50.000Z","msg":"推文回覆"},{"pid":"6c9ed4dfa4f5187b8070387ad9682b7f72a6b676","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:29:11.000Z","msg":"為求推post,不擇手段"},{"pid":"22af9f1dd93c3e8e37857cd1a2f22da8d0977243","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:29:28.000Z","msg":"係我唔啱係我錯"},{"pid":"cb00cc8de39bceeb7ecc2481cbc6bc51e3e40c10","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-01T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"每日一餐黃店食到好撚肥"},{"pid":"f693c1df631fa6cbf187ed9452c606940be4f0de","tid":2225830,"uid":29033,"like":0,"dis